Package fr.cnrs.iees.rvgrid.observer

Interface Observer

All Known Subinterfaces:
GridNode, StateMachineObserver
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGridNode, CtrlNode, SimNode, StateMachineController, StateMachineEngine
public interface Observer

An interface for objects that can observe an Observable, i.e. receive messages from it about its state.

This class must be overriden to implement the observer pattern.
